{"tid":1657740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"耿爽斥美方通過香港人權 但沒提中方採甚麼反制措施","createTime":"2019-10-16T08:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T16:23:48.000Z","uid":125168,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"0d8e370501c61def641862c2d39c83eaf5a5650a","tid":1657740,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:29:51.000Z","msg":"耿爽斥美方通過香港人權法　但沒提中方採甚麼反制措施<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人耿爽說，中方對美國國會眾議院執意通過所謂的「香港人權與民主法案」，表示強烈憤慨和堅決反對。但他在例行記者會，並無說明中方會採取甚麼反制措施。耿爽說，中方今天上午已經作出全面的回應，外交部發言人以及其他一些部門都已經做了表態。他強調，對於美方的錯誤決定，對於美方損害中方利益的錯誤行為，中方會採取有力的措施予以反制，堅定維護自身主權、安全、發展利益。<span style=\"color: red;\">至於具體舉措，他希望記者保持關注。</span><br />\n<br />\n2019-10-16 16:20:28 RTHK<br />\n<br />\n睇到支那咁嘅反應真係爽死了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7adaa32e0b90f6dc2151daea6e1a940dffd894b9","tid":1657740,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:30:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7eLY27V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7eLY27V.jpg&h=0bfc2f6e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"cc98762f09630abbd89ec049e8178404fa46f37a","tid":1657740,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:32:02.000Z","msg":"支那口交部已經一個反制措施都懶得作"},{"pid":"6c1775c9ff8bc69aedfaef73eb607ce19a0a1461","tid":1657740,"uid":15943,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:32:40.000Z","msg":"想射又射唔到果種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63c999e8338f49361145ae6eec7f26efee9401e","tid":1657740,"uid":10064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:32:54.000Z","msg":"諗唔到呀"},{"pid":"68ec5bb0aef2563d